@startuml US11-SSD
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US11 List Trains

autonumber

actor "Player" as Player
participant "System" as System

activate Player

Player -> System: list trains
activate System

System --> Player: displays list of trains grouped by locomotive type\nand sorted alphabetically by name
deactivate System

deactivate Player

@enduml 